devdoc.author: RabbitHole.gg
devdoc.details: This contract is used to render on-chain data for RabbitHole Receipts (ERC-721 standard)

generateTokenURI(uint256,string,uint256,.details: generates the tokenURI for a given ERC-721 token ID

params.claimed_: Whether or not the token has been claimed
params.questId_: The questId tied to the tokenId
params.rewardAddress_: The address of the reward token
params.rewardAmount_: The amount of reward tokens that the user is eligible for
params.tokenId_: The token id to generate the URI for
params.totalParticipants_: The total number of participants in the quest

returns._0: encoded JSON following the generic OpenSea metadata standard

humanRewardAmount(uint256,address).details: Returns a human readable reward amount

symbolForAddress(address).details: Returns the symbol for a token address
